314
00:41:20,565 --> 00:41:22,285
Za porušení svého slibu.

315
00:41:25,169 --> 00:41:25,903
Běžte.

316
00:41:27,423 --> 00:41:28,384
Počkejte.

317
00:42:00,491 --> 00:42:01,540
Počkejte

318
00:42:34,428 --> 00:42:35,462
konečně

319
00:42:38,297 --> 00:42:39,765
jsem to našel.

320
00:42:42,400 --> 00:42:43,681
Traipoom

321
00:42:45,123 --> 00:42:46,591
připrav si slzu,

322
00:42:51,867 --> 00:42:53,301
zničte vše.

323
00:42:53,658 --> 00:42:54,943
Nenechte nic z toho.

324
00:46:04,561 --> 00:46:05,276
Plai.

325
00:46:06,344 --> 00:46:07,296
Strýčku Ching.

326
00:46:09,037 --> 00:46:09,833
Plai.

327
00:46:13,124 --> 00:46:14,030
Plai.

328
00:46:14,556 --> 00:46:15,488
Strýčku Ching.

329
00:46:16,157 --> 00:46:17,089
Teto Cherdo.

