00:46:21,024 --> 00:46:21,857
Plai.

331
00:46:31,144 --> 00:46:32,504
Co se stalo?

332
00:47:07,274 --> 00:47:08,711
Odpočívej v pokoji.

333
00:47:24,023 --> 00:47:25,191
