446
00:56:55,811 --> 00:56:58,157
Co Plai a Cherda?

447
00:56:58,184 --> 00:56:59,330
Jsou ok.

448
00:57:00,626 --> 00:57:01,492
Stop!

449
00:57:01,801 --> 00:57:04,782
